---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Why Choose Us" id="why-choose-us">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    At <span class="text-primary">Nova Software Solutions</span>, we don't just build software — 
    we craft solutions designed to help your business thrive.
  </Fragment>
  <ul class="grid max-w-6xl grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:rocket-launch" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Fast Delivery</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        We work <span class="text-primary">quickly</span> without compromising on quality, 
        ensuring your project is delivered on time.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:currency-usd" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Competitive Pricing</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        Quality solutions at <span class="text-primary">affordable rates</span>, 
        giving you the best value for your investment.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:account-heart" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Client-Centric Approach</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        Your success is our priority — we <span class="text-primary">listen</span>, 
        we adapt, and we build exactly what you need.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:cogs" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Tailored Solutions</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        No cookie-cutter software — every solution is 
        <span class="text-primary">custom-built</span> to fit your unique needs.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:shield-check" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Reliable Support</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        From start to finish (and beyond), we’re here to 
        <span class="text-primary">support</span> you every step of the way.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 border border-default bg-offset p-6">
      <div class="size-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current p-3">
        <Icon name="mdi:lightbulb-on" class="size-full" />
      </div>
      <p class="text-center font-extrabold text-xl">Innovation-Driven</p>
      <p class="text-center text-offset text-sm">
        We embrace the latest tech to deliver 
        <span class="text-primary">modern, future-proof</span> solutions.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</ContentSection>
